  <w:body>
    <w:p>
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="Title"/>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Draft Board Memo</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Board Meeting Date: March 21, 2026</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Prepared by: Lena Ortiz, Interim CFO</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Distribution: Board of Directors</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>This memo summarizes the current launch recommendation for the Horizon Pantry product line and outlines the financing assumptions for the FY2026 planning cycle.</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="Heading1"/>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Executive Summary</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Management recommends proceeding with a regional launch in Q3. The current plan assumes a phased retail rollout, targeted category promotion, and disciplined working-capital management during the first two quarters after launch.</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>The operating plan remains contingent on margin discipline, retailer onboarding quality, and a measured release cadence across priority markets. Leadership requested that the board packet preserve all active assumptions while clearly separating them from archived planning language.</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:p>
      <w:pPr>
        <w:pStyle w:val="Heading1"/>
      </w:pPr>
      <w:r>
        <w:t>Financial Summary</w:t>
      </w:r>
    </w:p>
    <w:tbl>
      <w:tblPr>
        <w:tblStyle w:val="TableGrid"/>
        <w:tblW w:w="0" w:type="auto"/>
        <w:tblBorders>
          <w:top w:val="single" w:sz="8" w:space="0" w:color="auto"/>
          <w:left w:val="single" w:sz="8" w:space="0" w:color="auto"/>
          <w:bottom w:val="single" w:sz="8" w:space="0" w:color="auto"/>
